metadata.name: $BULLA #1
metadata.description:
BullaBeraNFT is your access to $BULLA. The more you have, the more $BULLA airdrop you get. Snapshot of your bags will be taken - time and date will be announced on our Twitter.

$BULLA LP will be funded by the BullaBera team + funds from mint. LP will be locked and contract will be renounced.

We are tired of NFT people used as exit liquidity. This time, it's all fair game.
